            "id": 5931322,
            "title": "外資再甩賣台積電3.3萬張 累計今年賣超31.6萬張、提款逾3000億元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股今 (9) 日開低走低，一路重挫跌破萬八大關，終場收在 17391 點，跌幅為 1068 點，改寫歷史第三大跌點紀錄，外資瞄準大型權值股進行調節，再賣台積電 3.3 萬張，今年以來已調節 31.6 萬張，累計提款金額高達 3019 億元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>三大法人合計賣超 459.71 億元，外資賣超 357.76 億元，呈現連二賣，投信轉買 1.24 億元，自營商也調節 103.19 億元，已連 8 賣；期貨方面，外資減碼空單 2206 口，未平倉空單口數降至 27871 口。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>外資賣超瞄準大型權值股，再度調節台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TSM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TSM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TSM-US</a>) 達 3.3 萬張，已連二天賣超，同步賣超鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>)2.9 萬張，其他如中鋼 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2002:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2002\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2002-TW</a>)、聯電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2303-TW</a>)、元大金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2885:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2885\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2885-TW</a>)、中信金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2891:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2891\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2891-TW</a>) 也都有 2 萬張以上的水準。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>外資買超則鎖定債券 ETF，買超前十名就有五檔，包括國泰 20 年美債 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00687B:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00687B\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00687B-TW</a>)、群益優選非投等債 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00953B:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00953B\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00953B-TW</a>)、元大美債 20 年 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00679B:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00679B\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00679B-TW</a>)、國泰 10Y + 金融債 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00933B:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00933B\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00933B-TW</a>)、凱基美國非投等債 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00945B:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00945B\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00945B-TW</a>)，五檔合計張數高達 32.5 萬張，其他則為如興 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4414:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4414\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4414-TW</a>)、新光金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2888:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2888\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2888-TW</a>) 與神達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3706:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3706\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3706-TW</a>)。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>投信、自營商皆與外資對作，反向敲進中信金與聯電，兩者合計買超 2.6 萬張、1.8 萬張。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
